snippet.title: Strider Mountain HL2 Mod PreRelease trailer
snippet.description: Strider Mountain HL2 Mod PreRelease trailer takes the player through Gordon Freeman's journey as high winds take him OFF COURSE, and he makes his way to the OUTPOST that sits at the base of StriderMountain.
